  "prompt": "I told her I like her, now what?",
  "response": "After expressing your feelings to her, the next steps depend on her response and your comfort level. Here are some suggestions on how to proceed:\n\n1. **Her Response**: Pay attention to how she reacts. Did she say she likes you back, needs time to think, or isn't interested? Her response will guide your next steps.\n\n2. **Give Her Space**: If she needs time to think about it, respect her space and don't pressure her for an immediate answer.\n\n3. **Continue Communication**: If she reciprocates your feelings, continue to communicate openly and honestly. Plan to spend more time together to strengthen your connection.\n\n4. **Stay Friends**: If she doesn't feel the same way, it's important to respect her feelings. You can decide if you want to remain friends or if it's too difficult for you emotionally.\n\n5. **Be Patient**: Relationships develop at different paces. Be patient and let things progress naturally.\n\n6. **Reflect on Your Feelings**: Regardless of her response, take time to reflect on your own feelings and what you want moving forward.\n\nRemember, it's important to handle the situation with maturity and respect, regardless of the outcome.",
